Criticism is perfectly welcomed but toxicity is not. When you join the telegram and start cursing at admins and shouting shit coin. I'm pretty sure any and all crypto telegrams would ban you. There is a proper way to voice concerns without being disrespectful.

That is not my aim. The goal is to all be on the same page and grow crypto adoption. Before I make any blanket statement, I do my due diligence before providing an opinion. You should do the same. It doesn't help the cause when you don't know what you're talking about!

Show me a statistic that shows adoption and use case that's greater than 2%? Do your parents own crypto? Your neighbors? Do most of your friends own crypto?
